---
title: Jamaican Jerk Salmon & Roasted Veggies  with Tomato Salsa & Lime Mayo
description: Let's give our blushing pink salmon the Jamaican jerk treatment! Warmly spiced and bursting with flavour, this delicate fish sits prettily alongside an array of roasted veggies. All you need is a generous drizzle of lime mayo to finish things off!

